name: arch of infinity worlds
description:
The arch of infinity worlds.
A mysterious passageway composed of countless arches, according to the legends that if you are brave enough to enter it you can discover the wonders of infinite worlds... will you join me on this journey into the unknown? 

This is where it all begins, an infinite journey through the cosmos and the possibilities of countless worlds and countless landscapes that I, jagger the traveler, will share with you.
